value.string: In this private, gated agricultural subdivision in Haiku lies a 1.26 acre parcel that’s ready to build a main home. Build site has both beautiful North Shore ocean and lush green valley views. Subdivision has private water system, this allows you to build the home you desire, and not restricted by fixture count. This is the main home portion of a two lot CPR.

A great deal in Haiku with full utilities and an ocean view. Lot has just been cleared and has good access via new driveway. Water meter and overhead power located on lot, great head start for any future structures. You can't see the lot from the street, you have to drive in at the top at new driveway. Private and secluded, yet 10 minutes to Hanzawas General Store and Haiku Marketplace. Zoned for large house and 1000 sq. ft. accessory dwelling and barns. Great lot for horses and livestock if you like critters.If you love trees, this place is for you.

Gorgeous 2 acre lot that's cleared on the interior and ready for your new home. This lot is very private and the perimeter of the property is surrounded by trees and natural vegetation. There's an old portuguese oven thats still standing from an old dwelling that used to be there. The general area is not tied in to county water so a catchment system will be needed. The lot is partially fenced and has a gated entry. Contact your local Realtor for more information or to view the property.
The Maui Real Estate Team, Inc

Awesome Kailua lot with a stream and small water fall. There are two excellent building spots one with a gorgeous view and another that is more secluded. Less than 35 minutes to the airport and a convenient drive to the shops and restaurants of Paia, Hookipa Beach park, Haiku and Makawao! Telephone and Electric are available, off the grid living is certainly an option. Water will be by catchment. This lot offers a rare opportunity for an adventurous spirit.
The Maui Real Estate Team, Inc

This is 3.8 acres of stunning land in Haiku. For those that want to get back to nature, start a small farm or just enjoy the quiet of the Maui countryside, look no further. The lot is situated at the end of a road bordering EMI land. It has been grazed by cattle for many years. The lot is almost all usable with just enough slope to make the ocean views that much more impressive. Water is to be provided by catchment. Produce your own electricity via the sun. This is one of the best opportunities on the market for buyers who want to live simply amidst the natural beauty of Maui’s North Shore.

Watch the waves breaking at Kuiaha Bay from this secluded 10.35 acre ocean view property, just minutes from Hookipa Beach, Hana Highway, & Haiku School on Maui’s North Shore. There is a perfect home-site near the gated entrance with an unobstructed ocean view. Down a rugged jungle road, multiple acres have been cleared for agriculture &/or building opportunities. In the flourishing gulch, prolific 75 year-old lychee trees dot the landscape. You will also find avocado, mango, lilikoi, coffee, rollinia, coconut palms, black bamboo, & edible bamboo shoots - all growing alongside a seasonal stream. Numerous areas for meditation bungalows & ag structures are available, or enjoy the private forest just to wander. Raise specialty livestock or boutique crops in this unique gulch, protected from Maui’s trade winds. Bring your walking shoes to see all the wonderful potential here! County water meter in place.

Beautiful private lot overlooking Maui's north shore. With pristine Haleakala and ocean views, there are multiple prime locations where you can build your off the grid home. This lot has stream frontage on Honokala Stream, great privacy easy access to Honokala Road which is in great condition after a recent re-grading. Nearby legal ocean access to the bay makes this property very interesting. Grow your own garden, fruit trees, build a few houses and barns and go get your dinner from the ocean. This place is ready for those with the survivalist gene in them. for Recently surveyed in Dec. 2015 shows no encroachments . If you think GPS and no Realtor are a good idea, remember that a 2,000 bull and his 25 cows live there. Adjacent 27 acres MLS 368232, oceanfront parcel is available for $2,500,000.

Bulid-ready, all usable, park-like with ocean, green gulch, and Haleakala views. $12,000 credit to Buyer for the relocation of the power lines underground. Water is private well, which allows you to build the home you want without fixture count restrictions. Easy access to Hana Hwy for quick trips to beaches, restaurants, and shops in Paia. Minutes to Ho'okipa. Seller requests 1031 exchange at no cost to the Buyer. Seller is licensed Real Estate Salesperson in the state of Hawaii. Some seller financing possible. Two dwellings allowed by County code. CPR likely possible.

Conveniently located in quiet, lush Haiku and boasting ocean and mountain views, this flat, gently sloping, two-acre zoned Rural RU-.5 lot is brimming with potential. The current county code for rural .5 land allows for one home for every half acre (please double-check with the county to verify this information); there is no water meter installed and there are no CC&Rs or HOA. The property rests at the end of a 20-foot-wide private road, just one minute from Haiku Town, 12 minutes from Pa'ia Town and 22 minutes from Kahului Airport. The lot has been surveyed and cleared--and it is ready to be sold. Call your favorite Realtor to schedule a showing of this hidden gem.

Seller Financing available. OCEANVIEWS. Incredible opportunity to own this wonderful parcel of land. Located in Kailua area of Hanawana. Multiple build-able sites. Easy to get to and only 25 minutes from Paia. Close enough to restaurants, beaches, and entertainment but still allows for privacy. Don't miss this wonderful private property with great views and gently sloping land which borders the forest reserve for privacy on the North Side. Leased County water for $100 per year. Electric to land. Majority of the property is buildable and thus 5 acres of buildable land is huge for this price. Don't miss this opportunity. All offers will be considered. Adjacent to Hana Highway and easy access. Build the home of your dreams. Check out the pictures and virtual tour. This is such a beautiful piece of paradise it is not to be missed. Hawaii Lenders are financing this size of land in Hawaii so now is the right time to buy.

This property offers end of road seclusion, expansive ocean, mountain, and crater views, peace and privacy, yet its only 5 minutes to picturesque Makawao Town! There are 3 level building sites with amazing views. This 5.75 acre CPR'd lot is surrounded by miles of ranch land, nature and wildlife. It has good soil, is fenced, gated and very conveniently located.(an easy 5 minute drive to Makawao Town's restaurants, art galleries, library and post office-8 minutes to Haiku Cannery-15 minutes to Hookipa Beach Park-20 minutes to the airport and Kahului). The condo documents allow for a 1000 sq.ft. home. Garage, barn, ag office, and other structures allowed as permitted by county. Driveway and water meter are in place. Ready to build. East to show, but not a drive-by.

Heavenly Haiku! Phenomenal Ocean and Haleakala views! This all-usable 2-acre parcel is situated in Windward Estates, one of Haiku’s top communities which features private, concrete roads and underground utilities. Enjoy privacy and construct your own beautiful, high-quality home on this easy building lot. Conveniently located just 7 minutes from Hookipa Beach Park and 15 minutes from Paia town. A County water meter is already installed. Maui Electric and cable high-speed internet services are readily available. Excellent climate with breezy, sunny days and sleepy, rainy nights. The fertile soil is great for keeping your flourishing gardens healthy and green. Remarkable homes and friendly neighbors. Ready for you to create your own comfortable Haiku Upcountry lifestyle. The EMI stream borders the property on its eastern boundary and offers great privacy. Call your favorite agent and set up your own private tour.

Private all usable land! This lot overlooks beautiful Kakipi Gulch with vast blue ocean views. Sunny location kept cool by the pleasant ocean breeze. Hike to Pilale Bay for swimming and fishing. Wonderful site to create your dream. Electricity on site. Smooth and easy county paved road to site. Sealed One piece 2500 gallon Polyethlene Water Tank. Co-listor is owner and a licensed Realtor in Hawai'i.

This large 22 acre parcel is in the John and Mary Phillips Subdivision, a gated community at end of Awalau Road past Haiku's Hanzawa Variety Store. Lot # 5 is the furthest back in the subdivision and on a cul-de-sac which provides exceptional privacy. It's the largest of 17 lots in the subdivision. This lot is a mix of relatively level land and steep terrain providing a delightful character. This community does not have an association to frustrate your home design. Design the home that suits yourself instead of someone else, get a building permit, and start building!

AMAZING, nearly ocean-front, private, 14.25 acres of land in a spectacular setting. Water meter installed. Expansive ocean and valley views, overlooking a tremendously long stretch of the north-shore shoreline and a beautiful cove. Feels like you’re on a hundred acres. Varied terrain, several nice building sites including two hill tops with privacy and sweeping views. Haleakala views too. Close to Paia, and Haiku School. Enter through a Haiku neighborhood, near to and across from the Haiku Community Center. Be patient driving along Kahiapo Place to come to this jewel at the end of the sometimes bumpy road. (The old lighthouse road abuts this property on the Paia side, a ways down but that roadway is no-longer driveable). Access is over an easement at the very end of Kahiapo Place and a bit tricky to locate. Please arrange for an appointment or ask for specific directions. Property can also be seen in the distance from Nahele Pl. Be sure to view the video.

Incredible Ocean Views on the North Shore of Maui! 6.96 gently sloping acres located on the "Makai" or Ocean side of Hana Hwy. Many large and mature trees including Eucalyptus, Cypress, Banana and more. Convenient location minutes to Haiku Town and just 10 minutes to the famous Ho'okipa Beach with world-renowned windsurfing, surfing and white sand beaches. On this Agricultural zoned lot you can build two dwellings: your dream house and a 1,000sf cottage. And, a big bonus is this lot may have the potential to do a 3 lot subdivision!

This 12 acre lot is located in Hamakualoa, the north shore of Maui near Pa'ia approximately 14 miles east of Kahului. Nearby beaches include Ho'okipa Beach, one of the world’s best windsurfing beaches. Ho'okipa is also a favorite hangout for kite surfers and surfers. The property boasts ocean and mountain views from several vantage points and is lush with fruit trees.
The Maui Real Estate Team, Inc

Sometimes the best things in life are hidden in plain sight. This 17 acre parcel of land situated on the ocean side of Hana Highway near Jaws fits that description to a T. With TWO county water meters installed, substantial Hana Highway frontage, and a perfect building site tucked away from the rest of the property, it is well positioned for agricultural or equestrian pursuits. The two water meters make a CPR possible which would be great for a Agri-Tourism venture. The building site features commanding ocean and East Molokai views and privacy. Call your Realtor to arrange a tour of this beautiful North Shore Acreage.

INCREDIBLE FARM & RANCH LAND CONSISTING OF APPROXIMATE 27.23 ACRES WITH A 1" WATER METER WHICH IS EXTREMELY VALUABLE. AN APPROXIMATE 40' x 110' UNPERMITTED CONCRETE BUILDING IN VERY GOOD CONDITION WITH A REPLACEMENT VALUE WORTH OVER $100,000. AN "AFTER THE FACT" PERMIT MAY BE A POSSIBILITY WITH COUNTY APPROVAL AND THE HELP OF AN ENGINEER. BUILDING WAS ONCE USED FOR A SUCCESSFUL PIGGERY. A SECOND UNPERMITTED & DILAPIDATED BUILDING ON A CONCRETE SLAB AND SEPARATE STALLS AS USED FOR THE PIGGERY STILL EXIST ON THE PROPERTY. THERE ARE TWO SEASONAL STREAMS THAT RUN THRU THE PROPERTY (OPAEPILAU AND AWALAU) AND AN EMI EASEMENT. MANY COFFEE TREES BORDER THE STREAM BEDS. THERE ARE SEVERAL CHERRY TREES WHICH ARE FRUIT BEARING DURING THE SEASON ALONG WITH NATIVE PLANTS & FLOWERS. ENTIRE PARCEL IS FULLY FENCED ALTHOUGH IT MAY NEED SOME REPAIRS. BEAUTIFUL PASTURE LAND PERFECT FOR GRAZING FARM ANIMALS, FARMING, ORCHARDS OR FOR A BUSINESS VENTURE. THE CENTER PLATEAU IS AN EXCELLENT LOCATION TO BUILD YOUR NEW RANCH HOUSE OFFERING DISTANT OCEAN VIEWS.

The Pacific Ocean stretches out to its vast expanse as you are instantly transported to a world of possibilities on this 2-acre lot. Located amongst some of the most impressive homes on the North Shore in the community of Aino O Ka Hale Pili, Hale Pili is in one of the private locations in the neighborhood. Let this spectacular setting be the inspiration for your dream home. Truly a legacy property. Call your favorite Realtor for a showing today.
